org.hypergraphdb.query

Interface HGAtomPredicate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    And, AnyAtomCondition, ArityCondition, AtomPartCondition, AtomPartRegExPredicate, AtomProjectionCondition, AtomRegExPredicate, AtomTypeCondition, AtomValueCondition, AtomValueRegExPredicate, DelayedSetLoadPredicate, DisconnectedPredicate, IncidentCondition, IsCondition, LinkCondition, Not, Or, OrderedLinkCondition, PositionedIncidentCondition, RABasedPredicate, SimpleValueCondition, SubgraphContainsCondition, SubgraphMemberCondition, SubsumedCondition, SubsumesCondition, TargetCondition, TypedValueCondition, TypePlusCondition, ValueAsPredicateOnly

    public interface HGAtomPredicate

    This interface defines a predicate of a single atom. There is no guarantee as to the running time of a predicate, but in general implementation should strive not to do explicit reads from the data store whenever possible.
